-- MOVES-Daniel Benatoff named Halcyon Asset Management (UK) co-head
-- 
-- Wed Oct 01, 2014 06:34AM EDT
-- None



Oct 1 (Reuters) - Investment manager Halcyon Asset Management LLC has promoted Daniel Benatoff to co-head of Halcyon Asset Management (UK) LLP.

Benatoff, who has been with Halcyon since May, will work alongside Damien Miller, who will join the firm by year-end, Halcyon said. [ID:nPn9jb7tW]